h3. Background of Request

When unauthenticated user access the following URL:

{code}
<Server Base URL>/plugins/servlet/confluence/placeholder/{code}

Confluence will provide a pop up WebDav authentication window as seen on this screenshot:

!WebDav.png|thumbnail!

The mentioned URL is not a valid URL that will lead to "WebPage not available" error or "page not found" message. Hence Confluence should not provide the pop-up at all and redirect the user directly to "WwebPage not available" error as describe here:

!wpa.png!

